{"tid":1010611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪我有問題？","createTime":"2019-02-06T06:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T17:38:34.000Z","uid":204020,"like":10,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"70b0233005e2c661514ae3eec4ff41c59600b529","tid":1010611,"uid":204020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"事源早前同女友分手，然後佢挽回既時候話承諾會減肥，會改善吾會成日講分手，我信左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來佢當然冇改善啦，我叫佢運動，佢又話要朝早做，4 5點就吾中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好啦，然後同啲fd打兩下排球又話做左運動，fine<br />\n去到最近行年宵，本身已經食左兩枝冰糖葫蘆<br />\n之後佢同我講，100蚊可以買四枝喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就話食咁多會肥，更何況你又冇做運動就完左個話題<br />\n翻去個陣，見到人飲老虎堂，佢又話想飲，我吾俾然後佢仲想拉我過去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我爆氣屌9佢，話你承諾過我既野冇做，而家又話飲珍珠奶茶？咁到底減乜撚野肥，最後佢同我講分手，話我係咁迫佢，話愛佢就吾會叫佢減，我就話你當初承諾會減，我同你講翻又話我係咁迫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:第一次開post<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"29e56bbdc52bf21b64baae6e5353efe19644296c","tid":1010611,"uid":204020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ab7bbb27d57dcbcd88249df252b2a70a516cfcb","tid":1010611,"uid":204020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd4540bd3fe703b4ad218efe1ed2e7d6c4c628e3","tid":1010611,"uid":204020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b539810f52cd05d34553f7621084c0e56973f73","tid":1010611,"uid":227457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔沒肥婆女朋友"},{"pid":"ac6bb4d6e0a7f35db1fdcf837ebc3842e17a6ea6","tid":1010611,"uid":204020,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"0b539810f52cd05d34553f7621084c0e56973f73","tid":1010611,"uid":227457